{"tid":1301381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[整合] 第一波抵制TVB 網絡攻勢","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:08:43.000Z","uid":258792,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3de69aae8df8f1cc6279c4dd4686c7a69181e5de","tid":1301381,"uid":258792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:30:16.000Z","msg":"今日係連登上面見到都有唔少人貼左寶礦力嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但除左係連登圍內打飛機之外<br />\n我地更需要發動一波網絡攻勢<br />\n一口氣將寶礦力推上社交媒體做成洗版<br />\n除左係多謝寶礦力抽廣告<br />\n<strong>更重要係令其他公司知道連登嘅力量</strong><br />\n<strong>要俾佢地知道, 而家係TVB到抽廣告就係最好嘅廣告</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考番最近嘅bottle cap challenge, 同之前嘅ice bucket challenge 等,<br />\n其實係ig 到出post 再tag 人<br />\n應該係一個好快做到社交媒體洗版嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以  不如就係IG發動一次抵制TVB洗版行動<br />\n<br />\n係唔同嘅寶礦力post 都見到有巴絲打係IG到po一支支, 甚至一箱箱嘅保礦力,<br />\n希望各位合作,<br />\n留番係聽日 7月10日 嘅晚上八點鐘開始<br />\n全港同步一齊po 手上嘅保礦力<br />\n再tag 身邊嘅三個朋友, <strong>遊戲玩法就係24小時內買寶礦力</strong><br />\n係香港發動一次 NoTVB Challenge<br />\n<br />\n係出post 嘅同時, 都可以統一番hashtag<br />\n我地要集中番 #NoTVB #antiTVB #thxPocari <br />\n<br />\n大家盡量出po, 而唔係用story 去做<br />\n咁樣個效果係更加好<br />\n<br />\n成效顯著<br />\n我地就可以每星期發動一次 NoTVB Challenge <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>邊間公司肯去抽廣告<br />\n連登仔就免費幫佢宣傳</strong><br />\n<br />\n相關帖文<br />\n寶礦力決定撤回TVB廣告 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1300186/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1300186/page/1</a><br />\n一人一支寶礦力集中貼圖區 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1300979/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1300979/page/1</a><br />\n我地要帶起一場hashtag感謝運動 eg寶礦力 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1300673/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1300673/page/1</a><br />\n呢一刻要買到寶礦力斷貨其他廣告商先會震驚跟風 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1300390/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1300390/page/1</a><br />\n寶礦力你收皮啦，出黎抽水！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1301013/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1301013/page/1</a><br />\n朋友 WhatsApp 證實 TVB 今次堅大鑊, 證明我地方向正確 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1301134/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1301134/page/1</a><br />\n[請每個人都幫幫手]正式宣佈第二波抵制TVB廣告行動開始!!!!!!!![置頂] <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1301015/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1301015/page/1</a><br />\n寶礦力開始斷貨！！！<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1300742/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1300742/page/1</a><br />\n「誠哥出招」百佳寶礦力一日（今日）快閃特價 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1300872/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1300872/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"dd898dcbfc4f474f2d808a98fbf78b991a97420e","tid":1301381,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"<code>7.10前 - 一人一信反DQ - Link 1</code><br />\n<code>7.10 - 19:00~22:30 - 麥小姐追思會 ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場🕊️</code><br />\n<code>7.11 - 14:00~22:00 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 ＠ 渣華道遊樂場🕊️</code><br />\n<code>7.11 -  油尖旺區議會夢遊 - Link 2</code><br />\n<code>7.13 - 15:30 - 光復上水 ＠ 上水花園第一號</code><br />\n<code>7.14 - 14:30~15:30 - 沙田區大遊行 ＠ 翠田街足球場</code><br />\n<code>7.21 - 將軍澳遊行</code><br />\n<code>7.27 - 紅磡土瓜灣遊行</code><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>Link 1: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/stopDQnow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FstopDQnow&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=3dd2cb8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/stopDQnow</a> / Link 2: <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=2a1e630b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ytm_dc711</a></em></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>撤回修例 收回暴動 撤銷控罪 追究警隊 雙真普選<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化</em></span></div>"},{"pid":"2519d2df79e23d60c95d99657e9f52ad94f0d6e8","tid"